1
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:14,020
♪Love crosses every cycle
of life and death♪

2
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,580
♪So let me fall with you♪

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,420
♪All the noise of the mortal world♪

4
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:24,060
♪Is nothing compared to her eyes♪

5
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Whoever said love itself is sin♪

6
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,020
♪When a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlight♪

7
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,180
♪Painting a banquet of
endless spring blooms♪

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
♪How beautiful♪

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode Five=

11
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:45,439
Prince Xuanlie!

12
00:00:50,119 --> 00:00:51,520
General, might I ask who you are?

13
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:53,759
I am

14
00:00:53,759 --> 00:00:57,560
Prince Xuanlie's betrothed,
his childhood sweetheart.

15
00:00:58,119 --> 00:00:59,359
Once the border is pacified

16
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:02,280
(Muye Luomei, Female General)
I'll be his rightful princess consort.

17
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:04,519
Greetings, General.

18
00:01:06,519 --> 00:01:08,000
The northern border conflict is dire.

19
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:10,319
His Highness is always burdened
with state affairs.

20
00:01:10,439 --> 00:01:11,920
Yet you, a mere wretched maid

21
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:15,400
dare seduce His Highness
with your tricks

22
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,760
and cloud his judgment.

23
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,400
Please understand

24
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,760
I was only making tea.

25
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:24,719
General, you're welcome to try some.

26
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,519
Still making excuses?

27
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:32,799
(The Muye family commands
hundreds of thousands in the north.)

28
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:35,159
(I can't afford to offend her.)

29
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,640
Luomei

30
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,200
the low being was making tea

31
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,680
and nearly scalded my hand.

32
00:01:41,719 --> 00:01:42,840
I was about to punish her

33
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:43,879
when you arrived.

34
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:51,159
So, a clumsy servant, is it?

35
00:01:51,519 --> 00:01:54,000
If so, she should be punished!

36
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:56,879
General...

37
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,480
Go on!

38
00:02:02,879 --> 00:02:04,000
She's been punished enough.

39
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,319
Come with me to the study.

40
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,400
The northern border matters most.

41
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:10,080
Don't waste time on a mere servant.

42
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:11,840
Let's go.

43
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:20,319
(Even if my life is worthless,)

44
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,719
(I'll tear a hole through the heavens!)

45
00:02:23,199 --> 00:02:24,439
(Just you wait,)

46
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,680
Murong Xuanlie!

47
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,439
Your Highness

48
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:32,360
General Muye has returned to the palace

49
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,719
and injured Princess Mei Lin.

50
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,240
Muye Luomei?

51
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,639
You dare hurt my girl?

52
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:45,280
Then you'll pay for it.

53
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:47,080
(General's Mansion)

54
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:47,879
(General's Mansion)
General,

55
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:49,319
someone sent you a gift.

56
00:02:56,980 --> 00:02:58,800
(Have Mercy)

57
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,400
(Have mercy?)

58
00:03:04,820 --> 00:03:06,700
(Have Mercy)

59
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:10,960
This is your deputy's head.

60
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,560
Just a small token today.

61
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:13,599
Next time

62
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,000
I'll deal with you too!

63
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:18,000
(It must be that wretch Mei Lin!)

64
00:03:43,199 --> 00:03:44,000
It seems

65
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:46,800
my brother only cares about power.

66
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:49,479
To win over the Muye family

67
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,680
he won't even protect you.

68
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,759
Without power and status

69
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:56,479
how could I compete with Muye Luomei?

70
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,159
It's not like
I can play your mother forever.

71
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:10,800
The Lockjaw Drop inside your body.

72
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,719
It's time for the antidote.

73
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,079
Beg me

74
00:04:16,879 --> 00:04:17,920
and I'll give it to you.

75
00:04:30,399 --> 00:04:32,199
Considering your injuries

76
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,319
lick it.

77
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:46,360
The dossier proving
you're the Xichu princess

78
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,519
has been forged

79
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,000
and submitted to Father.

80
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:51,959
Tomorrow, I'll petition Father myself

81
00:04:52,399 --> 00:04:54,240
to officially confer you
as Princess Anhe.

82
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,759
You'll have proper standing.

83
00:04:57,439 --> 00:04:59,000
Murong Xuanlie helped

84
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,759
distract Muye Luomei for you today.

85
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,680
That means you still have a chance.

86
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:07,319
Good.

87
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:13,279
By imperial decree

88
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:15,360
Mei Lin, Princess of Xichu

89
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:18,879
once offered her life
at the Drilling Ground.

90
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,199
Her loyalty is commendable.

91
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:22,680
She is hereby conferred
as Princess Anhe

92
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,639
and granted an imperial gold seal.

93
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,959
So decreed.

94
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:29,680
Thanks, Your Majesty, for your grace.

95
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:32,519
Long live Your Majesty!

96
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:35,120
Princess Anhe, please rise.

97
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:36,879
Thanks, Your Majesty.

98
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:39,560
I intend to host a banquet
for your investiture.

99
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:42,240
But if I leave it to my consorts

100
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:43,680
it may not suit your taste.

101
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,680
So

102
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,959
between Xuanlie and Jinghe

103
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,360
you may choose one to host it for you.

104
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,319
I'm new to the palace

105
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,800
and not familiar with things here.

106
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:08,079
But I've heard Lord Weibei
is a paragon of virtue.

107
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:11,120
I'm sure he'd arrange it well.

108
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:14,439
Very well.

109
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:16,519
Then Jinghe will handle it for you.

110
00:06:16,959 --> 00:06:17,680
Leave us.

111
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,199
Yes, Your Majesty.

112
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:33,040
Thank you for your help, Your Highness.

113
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,160
We've known each other a while.

114
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:36,800
No need for formalities.

115
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,240
Why did you choose Jinghe?

116
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,879
I promised you

117
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:41,879
the position

118
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:42,680
and your safety.

119
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:45,519
Why still entangle yourself
with a loser like him?

120
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:49,279
You've chosen General Muye,
Your Highness.

121
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:52,759
I won't trouble you further.

122
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:54,680
Are you still upset about Luomei?

123
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:58,639
Xuanlie, don't be too greedy.

124
00:06:58,959 --> 00:07:02,040
You can't have both, you know that.

125
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,800
Since you've already chosen

126
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,600
a betrothed with military power

127
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:08,360
stop bothering Mei Lin.

128
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:09,959
Let's go.

129
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:22,360
Murong Xuanlie now believes

130
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,959
I care for you deeply.

131
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:27,079
With his personality,
he will not let this go.

132
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,480
Next

133
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:33,199
don't disappoint me at the banquet.

134
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:39,740
(Night Banquet for the Princess)

135
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:44,480
Summon Princess Anhe to the hall!

136
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,519
I heard Princess Anhe

137
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,879
resembles the late Consort Chu.

138
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:50,920
Really? Is that so?

139
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:53,199
Then I must see how beautiful she is.

140
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:54,120
Indeed.

141
00:08:15,940 --> 00:08:17,900
♪Moonlight spills like quiet tides♪

142
00:08:18,150 --> 00:08:21,120
♪A celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edge♪

143
00:08:22,980 --> 00:08:24,460
♪Wings of light drift through the air♪

144
00:08:24,460 --> 00:08:28,140
♪Like blossoms that refuse to fade♪

145
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:31,940
♪It asks no right or wrong♪

146
00:08:32,180 --> 00:08:34,940
♪Nor fears the turning of fate♪

147
00:08:36,060 --> 00:08:37,660
♪A trace of spring on the wind♪

148
00:08:37,740 --> 00:08:40,300
♪A whisper of a broken heart♪

149
00:08:42,180 --> 00:08:44,260
♪A farewell song unfolds♪

150
00:08:44,540 --> 00:08:47,460
♪Carrying every sorrow within it♪

151
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:49,900
♪Karma weaves its endless thread♪

152
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:53,860
♪And I would follow you
without turning back♪

153
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:57,340
♪Life and death become
nothing sharp or final♪

154
00:08:57,660 --> 00:09:00,740
♪Love and hate are carried away
on the breeze♪

155
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:03,540
♪Before freedom is ever reached♪

156
00:09:03,540 --> 00:09:06,580
♪One must first dissolve into tears♪

157
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:10,260
♪Love crosses every cycle
of life and death♪

158
00:09:10,460 --> 00:09:13,580
♪So let me fall with you♪

159
00:09:13,780 --> 00:09:16,720
♪All the noise of the mortal world♪

160
00:09:16,820 --> 00:09:19,780
♪Is nothing compared to her eyes♪

161
00:09:20,380 --> 00:09:23,700
♪Whoever said love itself is sin♪

162
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:27,340
♪When a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlight♪

163
00:09:27,340 --> 00:09:30,020
♪Painting a banquet
of endless spring blooms♪

164
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:32,980
♪How beautiful♪

165
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:37,340
♪Two hearts leaning into one another♪

166
00:09:38,900 --> 00:09:40,860
♪Perfectly, impossibly right♪
